 When Alice requests GET /matching/recommendations?mode=nearby&limit=20\n    The
n the API should reject with code 1000\n    And the message should prompt comple
ting profile first\n\n  Scenario: User sees their matches\n    Given Alice has m
atched with Bob and Charlie\n    When Alice opens the match list\n    Then she s
